1.0.name: wordpress/gravity-forms-shootq-add-on
1.0.description: Photographers, your wait is over! The Gravity Forms ShootQ add-on utilizes the awesome capabilities of Gravity Forms to collect any information you desire and send it your ShootQ account as a new lead. It's easy to use, very flexible, and only attaches to the form or forms you need to use.
